TY  - JOUR
TI  - International Trade Theory in a Vintage-Capital Model
AU  - Bardhan, P. K.
AB  - [This paper contains an analysis of the pattern of comparative advantage in a model of growing international economy where intercountry productivity differentials are affected by, among other things, differences in economic life of machines in different countries.]
