TY  - JOUR
TI  - Optimum Growth in an Aggregative Model of Capital Accumulation: A Turnpike Theorem
AU  - Cass, David
AB  - [This paper presents an analysis of the behavior of growth paths which are optimum with respect to the social welfare generated by consumption over a finite planning period. The principal result is the establishment of a (modified) golden rule turnpike property for such paths.]
