TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Estimation of Nonlinear Econometric Systems
AU  - Eisenpress, Harry
AU  - Greenstadt, John
AB  - [The estimation of the parameters of a regression equation or system that is nonlinear in the parameters or the dependent variables, or both, is described. This is achieved without recourse to linearization. The OLS and FIML estimates are obtained by a stable modification of the Newton method.]
